snippet.title: Girls UND Panzer Dream Tank Match! Girl tank action rolling in! EN Announcement PV
snippet.description:
Announcement trailer for Girls UND Panzer Dream Tank Match.
Its roaring GIRL POWER with Girls Und Panzer, coming to Southeast Asia this coming winter. Look forward to lots of tank battle action!

Platform: PlayStation®4
Genre: Tank Action
Language: English Subtitles, Japanese Voiceover
